      <div class="portfolio-text-insert">
        <h1 class="scroll-medium">Branding</h1>
        <p>Kavaldon represents an uncompromising devotion to luxury fragrance. Each Kavaldon scent is a unique composition of the world's most lavish and exotic fragrances. Inspired by a mood, a memory, a touch, a Kavaldon candle will instantly ignite sophistication.  Hand-crafted and poured in Los Angeles, Kavaldon candles are the definition of luxury fragrance with refined style.</p>
        <div></div>
      </div>
